  <name>ASCII Images</name>
  <developer_name>ASCII Images Contributors</developer_name>
  <summary>Turn images into text</summary>
  
	<description>
	  <p>
	    ASCII Images uses jp2a to convert images into ASCII characters. 
	    You can save the output to a file, copy it, and even change its resolution!
	  </p>
	</description>
  
